Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.98,0:08:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,也许给你这个的人能帮到你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maybe whoever gave you that can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.28,0:08:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,打扰一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你的个案监督员会回答你的一切问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Your case supervisor can answer all your questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:08:55.29,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯  但我貌似没有监督员\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, I don't seem to have one of those.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只有一封事务办公室给我发的函\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just this letter from the Office of State Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.04,0:09:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,好的  女士\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.38,0:09:03.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我能帮您什么忙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How can I help?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.00,0:09:05.05,Default,,0,0,0,,在评估期间\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, during processing,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.05,0:09:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我问了我住在这里的亲人的情况\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I was inquiring about a family member living here,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.17,0:09:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,但一直没得到回复\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but I haven't heard anything since.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.55,0:09:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我很乐意为您效劳\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'd be happy to help you with that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,行尸破墙而入过后  墙会更加不稳固\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The wall's gonna be more fragile since they broke through.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:31.20,Default,,0,0,0,,大家越来越焦虑\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}People are getting anxious.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.49,0:09:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,北边聚集了行尸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There's dead on the north side.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我们通过敲墙来分散它们  起作用了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We're banging the wall to spread them out. It's working.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.24,0:09:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时的而已  它们会回来的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}For now, but they'll be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊  我们得彻底修好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, we need a long-term fix.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,工具有什么新进展吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Any update on tools?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.54,0:09:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,被戴皮者毁坏的还没能补回来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Still haven't replaced what the skins destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,而且我们的粮食又快吃完了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And we're back to square one on food.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.21,0:09:47.21,Default,,0,0,0,,剩下的马肉已经被腌上风干了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What's left of the horse has been salted and jerkied.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.21,0:09:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,那玩意不好吃  但依旧消耗得很快\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Stuff's nasty, but it's going fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.80,0:09:51.01,Default,,0,0,0,,山顶寨呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What about Hilltop?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.30,0:09:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,也许还有些打铁工具没被烧毁\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maybe some of the blacksmithing tools survived the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.22,0:09:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们几个人可以跑一趟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}A few of us can make a run,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:58.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-沿途还可以看看有没有猎物  -好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- maybe see if there's some game nearby while we're at it. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.64,0:10:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,如果什么都没了呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And if there's nothing left?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.65,0:10:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我们没法保证亚历山大的安全\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If we can't make Alexandria safe,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.94,0:10:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那我们就得开始考虑其他选项了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}we need to start thinking about other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.53,0:10:08.99,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历山大是我们的家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Alexandria's our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.11,0:10:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我还没准备好抛弃它\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm not ready to abandon ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.32,0:10:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还不行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.91,0:10:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得先努力拯救它\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We gotta fight to save it first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.63,0:10:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We should get moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.09,0:10:35.18,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人可能已经到哨站了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The others could already be at the outpost.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.47,0:10:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,也可能只剩咱俩了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Or it could just be us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.10,0:10:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你知道要想这次任务成功\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know the only way this works
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须相互信任吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}is if we trust each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.48,0:10:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能信任你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Why would I ever trust you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.15,0:10:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道  玛姬\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't know, Maggie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.36,0:10:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是因为你想活下来  我也一样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}'Cause you want to stay alive, same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我活了下来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If I stay alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.70,0:11:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那也是因为没有你  而不是因为你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}it'll be in spite of you, not because of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.50,0:11:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,老天啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.33,0:11:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你真这么觉得\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know, if -- if that's how you feel,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就不明白你为何还没干掉我了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't understand why you haven't put me down yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.93,0:11:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,靠\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我每天都会问自己这个问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I ask myself that question every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.07,0:11:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,靠\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.97,0:12:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,老天啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Jesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.56,0:12:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,快看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,基本上已经被洗劫一空了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Practically been picked clean.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.86,0:12:11.23,Default,,0,0,0,,可能不只有行尸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Might be more than the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.82,0:12:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,当心\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Heads up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.91,0:12:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,那些是我们的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Those are our people.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哥们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Dude...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.34,0:12:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,那是特洛伊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's Troy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.43,0:12:42.97,Default,,0,0,0,,快动手吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let's just get this done.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们得走了  -嗯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- We need to keep moving. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.03,0:13:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,注意周围\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Eyes open.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.29,0:13:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,预备  开始\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Ready? Start!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  再来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Good. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.26,0:13:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,保持中心姿态\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Center yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,重心放在后脚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Weight on your back foot.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,瞄准头部  刺\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Aim for the head, then stab!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.02,0:14:12.60,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  再来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Good. Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.60,0:14:14.36,Default,,0,0,0,,看啊  太疯狂了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Look. This is crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.36,0:14:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}God.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.28,0:14:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.49,0:14:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你们不应该那么做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You shouldn't be doing that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:33.46,Default,,0,0,0,,离开那里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Get away from there.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.63,0:14:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,冷静  我们只是在闹着玩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Calm down. We're just having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.92,0:14:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这很危险\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你们不停下  我就去告诉罗西塔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If you don't stop, I'm gonna tell Rosita.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.84,0:14:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴  你话太多了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Shut up! You talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.34,0:14:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,难怪你妈抛弃了你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No wonder your mom abandoned you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.81,0:14:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你说什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.22,0:14:49.43,Default,,0,0,0,,你真爱抱怨\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You're such a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.60,0:14:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定是厌倦了她整天叽叽歪歪的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She must've gotten tired of all her whining.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.94,0:14:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,再说一遍\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.57,0:15:01.78,Default,,0,0,0,,你敢不敢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I dare you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.74,0:15:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思  别\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Judith, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.17,0:15:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,离我远一点  你个变态\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Stay away from me, you psycho.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.09,0:15:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,看什么看\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What are you looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去不像是有人来过  所以说...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Doesn't look like anybody's been here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我们等着\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So we wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.29,0:16:33.12,Default,,0,0,0,,等多久\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How long?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.04,0:16:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,换做是你  你希望别人等你多久\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How long would you want someone to wait for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.92,0:16:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是觉得我们在这里待得越久\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I just think the longer we stay here,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,就越有可能被那些疯子抓到\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}the more likely it is that these lunatics catch us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.88,0:16:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,不如我们带着这些食物回去吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Look, how about we take this food back, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.43,0:16:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然没多少\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know it's not a lot,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.26,0:16:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但也算是有所收获了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but at least it's something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.68,0:16:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这根本不够\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.02,0:16:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得喂饱整个社区的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We need to feed a whole community.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.64,0:16:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,玛姬  你得学会及时放手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maggie, you need to know when to cut your losses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.94,0:17:06.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你所谓的放手...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Those losses...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.82,0:17:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,是指抛下我的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}are my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.24,0:17:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我懂  我真的懂\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I know. I do.
