Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.76,0:24:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,你当时那么小\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You were so small.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.43,0:24:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔希望你们有一段共同的回忆\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Carl wanted you to have a memory together.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.97,0:24:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,现在它坏了  他也走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Now it's broken, and he's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.48,0:24:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Everybody is.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.74,0:24:51.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我也很想他们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I miss them all, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:58.29,0:24:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,会变得轻松吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Does it get easier?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.96,0:25:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我说会  那就是在撒谎了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'd be lying if I said it did.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.34,0:25:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我担心我会逐渐忘记他们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm worried I'll start to forget about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.85,0:25:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,朱迪思\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Judith.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.78,0:25:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,其实我从没真正了解我爸\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You know, I never really knew my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.66,0:25:33.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我妈去世时\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And my mom died when...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.33,0:25:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我比你现在大一点\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I was a little older than you are now.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.16,0:25:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我仍经常想念她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I still miss her all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.71,0:25:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,我们相依为命了很长一段时间\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}For a long time, it was just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.42,0:25:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,经常搬家  换工作\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And we moved a lot, from job to job.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.76,0:25:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但她总能让我们继续前进\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But she always managed to keep us going.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.64,0:25:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我当时还不知道  但是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I didn't know it then, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.31,0:25:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,她是在教我如何靠自己生存\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}she was teaching me to survive on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.98,0:26:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哪天她要是不在了  我也能好好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So I'd be okay if she ever wasn't there.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.07,0:26:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,卡尔和你爸为你做了同样的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And Carl and your dad did the same thing for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.95,0:26:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,让你总能度过难关\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So you'd always be able to get though the tough times.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.46,0:26:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,木板固然不错\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Pieces of wood are nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.50,0:26:27.38,Default,,0,0,0,,但你不需要这个来记住他们有多爱你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But you don't need that to remember how much they loved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.43,0:26:36.06,Default,,0,0,0,,再说  我很擅长修东西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Besides, I'm really good at fixing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.73,0:26:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,你叫什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Name?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.69,0:26:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,别拿阿尔法或贝塔那种狗屁名字糊弄我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And don't give us any of that Alpha/Beta garbage, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.32,0:26:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,基斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Keith.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.61,0:26:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我叫基斯\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.32,0:26:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,-你来这里干什么  基斯  -我没伤人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- What are you doing here, Keith? - I'm not hurting anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.45,0:26:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,回答问题\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just answer the question.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.37,0:26:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔法死去后  人群四散而逃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}A-After Alpha fell, the herd scattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.54,0:27:01.83,Default,,0,0,0,,那些没被杀死或烧死的都走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Those who weren't killed or burned are gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.83,0:27:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,只剩下我一个\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm all that's left.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.04,0:27:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你没见过其他人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You haven't seen anyone else?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:03.96,0:27:05.04,Default,,0,0,0,,没有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.50,0:27:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,那你为什么留着尸群\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Then why do you keep the walkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.30,0:27:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,作为保护  慰藉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Protection, comfort.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.22,0:27:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,旧习难改\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Old habit.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.26,0:27:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么想\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:13.76,0:27:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我见过的低语者都是骗子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I think I haven't met a Whisperer who wasn't a liar.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.39,0:27:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那玛丽呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What about Mary?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.27,0:27:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你就相信她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You believed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.18,0:27:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么知道他在说谎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How do you know he's lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.23,0:27:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,你凭什么确信他没说谎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What makes you so certain he isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.06,0:27:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你有多了解他\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How well do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.94,0:27:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是我母亲核心集团里的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He wasn't part of my mother's inner circle.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.28,0:27:30.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他怕她\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He was afraid of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.61,0:27:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那只能证明他有眼睛  仅此而已\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, that proves he's got eyes, not much else.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.65,0:27:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,莉迪亚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Lydia.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.32,0:27:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我在漫长的冬天曾趁阿尔法不注意\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I snuck food to you during the long winters
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.49,0:27:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,偷送食物给你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}when Alpha wasn't looking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.79,0:27:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,你还记得吗  告诉他们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You remember? Tell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.50,0:27:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.09,0:27:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,看来她并没有那么了解你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Guess she doesn't know you that well after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.88,0:27:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这无所谓\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It doesn't matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.13,0:27:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,我母亲死了  他没伤人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}My mother's dead. He's not hurting anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.42,0:27:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,不  他有所隐瞒\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, he's hiding something.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.22,0:27:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,你觉得是陷阱吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You think it's a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.22,0:27:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是也不奇怪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Wouldn't put it past him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:00.18,0:28:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,亚伦说得对  我们得确保他不是个威胁\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Aaron's right. We need to make sure he's not a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.43,0:28:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,在我们决定如何处置他之前  先把他关进地窖\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let's get him into the cellar until we decide what to do with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.06,0:28:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,不  不要\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No. No!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.12,0:28:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,-哥们  -怎么了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Dude... - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.37,0:28:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,不会是好事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Nothing good.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.13,0:28:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他不是一个人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.89,0:28:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,看看他还说了什么谎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let's see what else he lied about.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.63,0:29:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还有多少人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How many more?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.42,0:29:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.55,0:29:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,外面还有多少你们的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How many more of you are out there?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.34,0:29:18.13,Default,,0,0,0,,就这些人  我发誓\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is it, I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.38,0:29:19.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你以为我会相信吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You expect me to believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.93,0:29:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚才当着我面说谎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}After you just lied to my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.89,0:29:22.97,Default,,0,0,0,,亚伦  你看他们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Aaron, look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.39,0:29:26.52,Default,,0,0,0,,他们很害怕  只是想重新当人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They're scared. They're just trying to be people again.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.52,0:29:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们也可能是威胁  藏在眼皮底下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Or they're a threat, hiding in plain sight
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.06,0:29:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,等待他们的人回来伏击我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}before their people come back and ambush us.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.56,0:29:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,我们并不全是冷血怪物\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We weren't all monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.03,0:29:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你  求你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Please. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.78,0:29:40.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这是娜比拉的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is Nabila's.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.62,0:29:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,-杰瑞  -别说了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Jerry... - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.54,0:29:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,他们曾潜入亚历山大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They were in Alexandria.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.70,0:29:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,烧毁了我们的家\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}They burnt down our home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.71,0:29:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What do you wanna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:59.26,0:30:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,当心\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.66,0:30:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,轮到我了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}My turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.36,0:30:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(271,81)\bord1\fs18\b1}西二楼  法律部\N\N北二楼  通讯部\N\N西一楼  安保部
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.53,0:31:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你既会使剑又会射箭吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You're -- You're a swordswoman and an archer?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.20,0:31:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  必要时我还很擅长用弹弓\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah, I'm pretty good with a slingshot, too, in a pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:47.58,0:31:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,对一个律师来说很不错了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not bad for a barrister.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:50.58,0:31:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,你变化很大  由美子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Wow. You've changed, Miko.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:53.83,0:31:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你也是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.34,0:31:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么找到这地方的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How did you even find this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.38,0:32:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(291,80)\bord1\fs14\b1\alpha&H20&}凯茜的万花筒\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N\N种子
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.92,0:32:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,灾变刚发生时  我逃离了芝加哥\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I fled Chicago when things first started going bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.64,0:32:07.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我给你留了那通语音信息后\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}After I left you that voicemail,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.18,0:32:09.56,Default,,0,0,0,,就开车向东走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I got in a car and headed east.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:10.06,0:32:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里以北20英里的地方没油了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Ran out of gas about 20 miles north of here
Dialogue: 0,0:32:12.68,0:32:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,但我很幸运  遇到了一些好人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but got lucky enough to link up with some good people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.10,0:32:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们很早就来到这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We all wound up here pretty early on
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.56,0:32:21.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那时弥尔顿一家刚把这里打造成避风港\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}when the Miltons made this place a safe haven.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.19,0:32:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,一开始只是几个安全街区\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It started with a few secure blocks,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.49,0:32:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,但之后社区一点点地\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but the community's been expanding
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.41,0:32:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不断扩大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}a little at a time ever since.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.16,0:32:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我几乎忘了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I, uh -- I almost forget
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.70,0:32:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,墙外的情况\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}what's going on outside these walls.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.92,0:32:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你一直以来就待在这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}And you've just been here this whole time,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:41.88,0:32:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,做蛋糕吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}just making cakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.51,0:32:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢烘焙  那使我快乐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I like baking. It makes me happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.47,0:32:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,-托米  你以前可是外科医生  -不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Tomi, you were a surgeon. - Hey, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.43,0:32:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托  现在别说这个\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Please, not now.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.80,0:32:50.81,Default,,0,0,0,,但你可以救死扶伤\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But you could save people.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.81,0:32:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在试图操纵别人的生活吗  由美子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Still trying to run people's lives, Miko?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.48,0:32:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我没想挑事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm not trying to start anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.48,0:33:01.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我只想要你过好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I just want what's best for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.07,0:33:04.86,Default,,0,0,0,,你上次见我快乐是什么时候  由美子\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}When was the last time you saw me happy, Miko?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.49,0:33:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,真正心满意足\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Truly content?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.66,0:33:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,记不起来了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Can't remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.16,0:33:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,也许是现在吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Maybe now.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.49,0:33:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢现在的生活\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I like my life the way it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.96,0:33:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,这是世界末日带给我的唯一礼物\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It's the one gift I got out of the world falling apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:21.54,0:33:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托你别毁了这一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Please, don't ruin this for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.80,0:33:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我当然不会了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Of course I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.84,0:33:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你只用告诉我一件事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Look, just tell me one thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.64,0:33:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方真有看起来那么好吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is this place really as good as it seems?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.39,0:33:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,比那更好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.19,0:33:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,如果我想替人求助的话  在这里可以做到吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So if I wanted to get help for people, I could do that here?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.82,0:33:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,一切皆有可能  只要你遵守规则\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Anything's possible, as long as you follow the rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.24,0:33:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,想吃蛋糕吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Want some cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.78,0:33:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,当然\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hell yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.04,0:34:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,没想到会在这遇见你  默瑟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Fancy meeting you here, Mercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.88,0:34:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方显然有个健身房\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, they clearly got a gym in this joint.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.63,0:34:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身材真完美\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Your chiseling is perfecto.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.01,0:34:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思  我要进去办事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Uh, excuse me. Got business inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.76,0:34:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,等等\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Wait, wait, wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.85,0:34:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我想感谢你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I... I wanted to thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.77,0:34:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,谢我什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}For what?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.44,0:34:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,谢你把这个还给我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}For making sure this got back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:24.82,0:34:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,不用谢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No need.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:26.73,0:34:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我只是把你的财物还给你  "公主"\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just returning your property, "Princess."
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.12,0:34:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还有别的事吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Was there something else?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.28,0:34:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,有\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.16,0:34:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你的睫毛美极了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You have really beautiful eyelashes.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.72,0:34:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉我其他人去哪了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Tell me where the others went.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.26,0:34:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在哪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.26,0:34:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还有多少人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}How many more?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.10,0:35:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,回答我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.99,0:35:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,莉迪亚  救我  求你了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Lydia, help me! Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.36,0:35:14.74,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在哪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.37,0:35:18.16,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔法没看错你们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Alpha was right about you people.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.24,0:35:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们假装自己高死人一等\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You pretend you're better than the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.00,0:35:22.83,Default,,0,0,0,,但死人很诚实\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But dead is honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.96,0:35:25.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你们的朋友们死了更好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Your friends are better off.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.48,0:35:47.31,Default,,0,0,0,,你离死不远了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}See, the clock's ticking now.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.69,0:35:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉更好了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do you feel better off?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.40,0:35:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以帮你\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Or I can help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.36,0:35:57.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以在感染扩散  你转变之前砍掉你的手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I can cut off your hand before the infection spreads and you turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:59.70,0:36:00.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要这样吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Would you like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:02.04,0:36:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,时间不多了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We don't have much time.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.33,0:36:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,-求你了  -他们在哪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Please... - Where are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.17,0:36:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我发誓我不知道  你一定要相信我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't know! I swear! You have to believe me...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.09,0:36:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,低语者仍是个威胁吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Are the Whisperers still a threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.42,0:36:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-不是  -别说谎\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- No! - Stop lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.80,0:36:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,-亚伦  够了  -不  我要答案\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}- Aaron, enough! - No, I need answers!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.97,0:36:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不  你要的是别的东西\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No, you want something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.14,0:36:20.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想在这里眼睁睁看着\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't have to be here to watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.97,0:36:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,再来\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Again.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.02,0:36:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,说实话吧  哥们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Just tell the truth, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.78,0:36:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要我说什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What do you want me to say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.03,0:36:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,之前确实有更多人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}There were more of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.86,0:36:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但他们都走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But they -- they're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.08,0:36:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I don't know!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.00,0:36:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,你他妈在做什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What the hell are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.75,0:36:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,阻止你再做会后悔的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Stopping you from doing something else you're gonna regret.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.50,0:36:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我在做必要的事  以保护每个我爱的人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm doing what I have to to keep everyone I love safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.34,0:36:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,你最应该理解的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You of all people should understand that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.13,0:36:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不该像这样做\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.97,0:36:58.05,Default,,0,0,0,,看看周围\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Look around.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.59,0:37:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们正站在低语者\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We are standing on the ashes
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.93,0:37:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,所毁掉的一切的灰烬上\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}of what the Whisperers destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.52,0:37:06.60,Default,,0,0,0,,正是因为他们  格雷西正在挨饿\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Gracie is going hungry because of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.65,0:37:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这个世界充满了不可救药之人\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}The world is full of people who are beyond saving,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.28,0:37:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不想等着他们上门找我们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and I am not gonna wait for them to show up at our doorstep.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.53,0:37:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,不\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.95,0:37:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,亨利的遭遇...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What happened to Henry...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.70,0:37:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,我之后的心情...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and how I felt after...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.08,0:37:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,控制了我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}it controlled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.54,0:37:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我任由自己走上了一条非常黑暗的道路\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I let it take me down a very dark path.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.71,0:37:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我伤害了我在乎的人们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}People that I care about were hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.67,0:37:36.34,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不管我做什么  我都难以释怀\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Now everything that I do, I carry that.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.97,0:37:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,你不想走这条路的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This is a path you don't want to go down.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.10,0:37:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,放他走吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Now you let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.68,0:37:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,放他走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let him go.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.33,0:38:10.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以砍掉你的手  你自己来也行\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I can cut your hand off or you can do it yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.63,0:38:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,你选吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Choice is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.93,0:38:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.81,0:38:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我说过我会找到的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Told you I'd find it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.64,0:38:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,这里吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Right here?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.69,0:38:33.69,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历山大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Alexandria.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.94,0:38:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,亚历山大  我是尤金  回话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Alexandria, this is Eugene. Come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.36,0:38:38.86,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金  尤金  你没事吧\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Eugene! Eugene, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.32,0:38:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,罗西塔\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Rosita?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.49,0:38:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,听到你的声音太好了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, it's dang good to hear your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:43.41,0:38:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,同感  朱迪思在我身边\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You too. I got Judith here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.95,0:38:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  你们都安全吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hi. Are you all safe?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.70,0:38:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你好  朱迪思\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hello! Hey, Judith.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.62,0:38:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是的  我们都安全  我们挺好的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yes, we're all safe. We're doing okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.17,0:38:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,那边情况如何\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Uh, how are things there?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.46,0:38:57.80,Default,,0,0,0,,战争结束了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Well, the war's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.80,0:39:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,阿尔法和贝塔死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Uh, Alpha and Beta are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.55,0:39:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但亚历山大一片狼藉  而且我们快没食物了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But... Alexandria's trashed, and we're running out of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.26,0:39:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起  我没听清...\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm sorry. I didn't get --
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.60,0:39:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Yeah. Eugene?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.27,0:39:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金  你还在吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Eugene, are you still there?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.40,0:39:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,尤金  你在哪\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Eugene, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.48,0:39:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,断了吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Is he gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.07,0:39:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,出故障了  没信号了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Something's haywire. Lost the feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.07,0:39:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,试试高频\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Uh, try a higher frequency.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.07,0:39:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,手举起来  远离无线电\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hands up! Move away from the radio.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.66,0:39:29.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我保证我没造成任何损害\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}No harm's been done, I can assure you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.62,0:39:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你被捕了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You're under arrest...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.67,0:39:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,罪名是未经许可使用政府财产\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}...for the unauthorized use of government property.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.32,0:40:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.74,0:40:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我要走了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm leaving.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:10.79,0:40:12.50,Default,,0,0,0,,不准拿走补给\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Not with those supplies you aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.50,0:40:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,我要把它们带回亚历山大\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm taking them back to Alexandria.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.62,0:40:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这个任务没有失败\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}This mission isn't finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.67,0:40:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,对我来说失败了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}It is for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.30,0:40:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,住手\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.95,0:40:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,天啊  你们到了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Oh, my God. You made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:52.95,0:40:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你们还好吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.33,0:40:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,更好更坏都经历过\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Been better. Been worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.79,0:40:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Same.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.21,0:40:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我们在树林里遇到了彼此\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We found each other in the woods.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.58,0:41:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,确保了没人跟踪我们来这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Made sure no one followed us back here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.34,0:41:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,很好  坐下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Good. Sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.84,0:41:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不知道你是否还活着\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We...didn't know if you'd survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.05,0:41:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果你活着  一定会在这里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}But if you did, knew you'd be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.43,0:41:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,其他人呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}What about the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.64,0:41:18.40,Default,,0,0,0,,邓肯  阿加莎  科尔  他们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Duncan, Agatha, Cole, they're --
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.56,0:41:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,他们死了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.28,0:41:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,奥尔登\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Alden's hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:24.32,0:41:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,他躲在一座教堂里\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He's holed up in a church somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.61,0:41:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,达里尔和弗罗斯特我不清楚\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Daryl and Frost, I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.82,0:41:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那么\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So then...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.12,0:41:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们等\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}we wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.42,0:41:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,我们等\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.60,0:41:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,完蛋了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Holy shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.22,0:41:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,我毁了一切\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I've ruined everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:58.39,0:41:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:06.03,0:42:08.32,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一起在火车站的那个年轻女人呢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Where is the young woman that was with me at the train station?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.36,0:42:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,特此通知  你们被控\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You are hereby notified that you're being charged
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.41,0:42:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,肆意闯入  鲁莽危害\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}with wanton trespassing, reckless endangerment,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.99,0:42:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,与外界组织非法通信\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and illegal communication with a foreign entity --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.41,0:42:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,全都是违反\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}all violations of Article 4,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.79,0:42:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,《联邦刑法》第4条第2节的行为\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Section 2 of the Commonwealth criminal code.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.34,0:42:26.92,Default,,0,0,0,,你们已获准在一小时内参加法官听证会\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You've been granted a hearing before a judge within the hour.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.96,0:42:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,如被判有罪  你们将被送到\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If found guilty, you will be dropped off
Dialogue: 0,0:42:29.30,0:42:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,远离城墙的区域  永久驱逐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}in a zone far outside our walls and banished from ever returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.10,0:42:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们这样做是有正当理由的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We did what we did for good reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.72,0:42:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你允许我们解释一下\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If you'd just let us explain --
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.85,0:42:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,跟法官说去吧  虽然这没用\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Tell it to the judge, although it won't matter,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.10,0:42:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你们来这里还不到一天\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}especially since you've been here less than a day
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.85,0:42:41.35,Default,,0,0,0,,已经违反了好几条法律\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}and already broken several laws.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.40,0:42:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我们要和律师谈谈\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We wanna talk to our lawyer.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.94,0:42:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,你们有律师吗\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You have an attorney?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.23,0:42:47.44,Default,,0,0,0,,当然有了  还是个厉害的律师\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Damn right we do. A fancy one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.57,0:42:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,既然这地方痴迷于规矩\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}So if this place likes rules so much,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.49,0:42:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,那你一定要允许我们找律师  这是我们的权利\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}you have to let us have one. It's our right.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.36,0:42:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,公民才有权利\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Rights are for citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:52.82,0:42:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是寻求庇护者\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You're asylum seekers.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.58,0:42:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,特权是靠自己争取的\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Privileges come when you've earned them.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.25,0:42:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Please, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.21,0:43:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,让我和史蒂芬妮谈谈\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}let me talk to Stephanie.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.75,0:43:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,她可以为我们做担保\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She can vouch for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.38,0:43:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,她正在单独接受评估和指控\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}She's being processed and charged separately,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.71,0:43:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,作为一个公民\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}as a citizen.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.71,0:43:09.13,Default,,0,0,0,,这太扯了\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}That's some bullshit.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.13,0:43:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,交给我吧  约翰\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'll take it from here, John.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.02,0:43:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,放他们走\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Let them go.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:24.73,0:43:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,霍恩斯比先生  我做不到  他们在候审\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Mr. Hornsby, I can't. They're awaiting trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.98,0:43:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,别碰他们\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Do not move them.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.03,0:43:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我去找墨瑟\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm going to find Mercer.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.17,0:43:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,等等  他是不是那个\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Wait. Was that...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.88,0:43:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,俗气录像男\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Cheesy video guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.51,0:43:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们可以信任霍恩斯比\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Hornsby is someone that you guys can trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.01,0:43:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.68,0:43:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,别急着谢我\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't thank me so fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.05,0:43:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,他也许能阻止你们被驱逐\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}He might be able to stop you from being banished,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.68,0:44:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,但你们不会安然无恙\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}but it won't be scot-free.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.31,0:44:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,你们仍要为所做的事付出代价\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}You'll have to pay for what you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.85,0:44:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不论以哪种方式\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}One way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.77,0:44:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,对这一切我很抱歉\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I'm sorry about all this.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.40,0:44:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我理解\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.65,0:44:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟他的人失去了很多\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}After all his people have lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.57,0:44:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,如果阿尔法还活着  她会做更糟糕的事\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}If Alpha were still here, she would've done worse.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.71,0:44:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,给你的  蘑菇\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}For you -- mushrooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.12,0:44:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,给你和其他人吃\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}For you and the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.04,0:44:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,感谢你送我这个  还有你之前说的话\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Thank you -- for this and for what you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.09,0:44:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不是都像她一样\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}We weren't all like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.72,0:44:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我们中有些人只是想生存\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Some of us just wanted to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.56,0:44:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,永远别回头\N{\fs14\fn微软雅黑\b0\3c&H202020&\shad1}Don't ever look back.
